:: CheckReflection {"position":"500,1900","size":"100,100"}
{(set: $madnessLogic to $madnessLogic + 2)}

You look down at your reflection in the crystalline water.

It's not quite right. The movements lag slightly, or move too soon, or move in ways you didn't move.

Your reflection's eyes hold an intelligence that feels separate from yours. It's studying you the way you're studying it.

Then it smiles, though you didn't smile.

The water ripples, distorting the image, but when it settles, your reflection has Natasha's face, and Natasha's reflection has yours.

[[Continue->AlarmNatasha]]


