You ignore the sound in your ears.

The pieces shift positions on their own, repeating the same sequence over and over. No move leads to a victory. No move leads to an end.

The king lowers its head.

For the first time since entering the dream, something here feels tired. You begin to get a peek of Theodore’s depression.




[[(Explore the zone further)->ContinueDreamTheo2]]

